build for javascript backend

# URL Shortener — Stress Test App #3
# Tests: redirect logic, hit counting, rate limiting, random code generation

# --- Data ---

create data shape Link:
  code is text, unique
  url is text, required
  hits is number, default 0
  created_at is timestamp, auto

# --- Endpoints ---

when user calls POST /api/shorten receiving link_data:
  validate link_data:
    url is text, required, min 1
  rate limit 10 per minute
  define new_link as: save link_data as Link
  send back new_link status 201

when user calls GET /api/links:
  define all_links as: look up all records in Link table
  send back all_links

when user calls GET /api/links/:code:
  define found as: look up records in Link table where code is incoming's code
  send back found

when user calls DELETE /api/links/:code:
  this endpoint requires auth
  remove from Links where code is incoming's code
  send back 'deleted'
